*busybox-1.00_pre6 (03 Feb 2004)

  03 Feb 2004; <solar@gentoo.org> busybox-0.50.ebuild, busybox-0.60.2.ebuild,
  busybox-0.60.3-r1.ebuild, busybox-0.60.3.ebuild, busybox-0.60.5-r1.ebuild,
